{"id":252,"parent_id":250,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":252,"title":"2 Peter 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Pet.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","False teachers among the Saints are damned—Lustful Saints will perish in their own corruption."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.1","order":"03.24.002.26050"},["b","1"],"But there were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"false prophets"],"also among the people, even as there shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"false"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"teachers"],"among you, who privily shall bring in damnable heresies, even denying the Lord that",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"bought"],"them, and bring upon themselves swift destruction."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.2","order":"03.24.002.26051"},["b","2"],"And many shall follow their pernicious ways; by reason of whom the way of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"truth"],"shall be evil spoken of."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.3","order":"03.24.002.26052"},["b","3"],"And through covetousness shall they with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"feigned"],"words make merchandise of you: whose",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"judgment"],"now of a long time lingereth not, and their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"damnation"],"slumbereth not."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.4","order":"03.24.002.26053"},["b","4"],"For if God spared not the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"angels"],"that sinned, but cast",["i","them"],"down to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"hell"],", and delivered",["i","them"],"into chains of darkness, to be reserved unto",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"judgment"],";"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.5","order":"03.24.002.26054"},["b","5"],"And spared not the old world, but saved",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"Noah"],"the eighth",["i","person,"],"a preacher of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"righteousness"],", bringing in the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"flood"],"upon the world of the ungodly;"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.6","order":"03.24.002.26055"},["b","6"],"And turning the cities of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Sodom"],"and Gomorrha into ashes condemned",["i","them"],"with an overthrow, making",["i","them"],"an",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"ensample"],"unto those that after should live ungodly;"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.7","order":"03.24.002.26056"},["b","7"],"And delivered just",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Lot"],",",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"vexed"],"with the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"filthy"],"conversation of the wicked:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.8","order":"03.24.002.26057"},["b","8"],"(For that righteous man dwelling among them, in seeing and hearing,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"vexed"],["i","his"],"righteous soul from day to day with",["i","their"],"unlawful deeds;)"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.9","order":"03.24.002.26058"},["b","9"],"The Lord knoweth how to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"deliver"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"godly"],"out of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"temptations"],", and to",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_9d"},"reserve"],"the unjust unto the day of",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_9e"},"judgment"],"to be punished:"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.10","order":"03.24.002.26059"},["b","10"],"But chiefly them that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"walk"],"after the flesh in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"lust"],"of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"uncleanness"],", and despise",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"government"],".",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_10e"},"Presumptuous"],["i","are they,"],"selfwilled, they are not afraid to speak evil of dignities."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.11","order":"03.24.002.26060"},["b","11"],"Whereas angels, which are greater in power and might, bring not railing accusation against them before the Lord."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.12","order":"03.24.002.26061"},["b","12"],"But these, as",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"natural"],"brute beasts, made to be taken and destroyed, speak evil of the things that they understand not; and shall utterly",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"perish"],"in their own corruption;"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.13","order":"03.24.002.26062"},["b","13"],"And shall receive the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"reward"],"of unrighteousness,",["i","as"],"they that count it",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"pleasure"],"to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"riot"],"in the day time. Spots",["i","they are"],"and blemishes, sporting themselves with their own deceivings while they feast with you;"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.14","order":"03.24.002.26063"},["b","14"],"Having eyes full of adultery, and that cannot cease from sin; beguiling unstable souls: an heart they have exercised with covetous practices; cursed children:"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.15","order":"03.24.002.26064"},["b","15"],"Which have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"forsaken"],"the right",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"way"],", and are gone",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"astray"],", following the way of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_15d"},"Balaam"],["i","the son"],"of Bosor, who loved the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_15e"},"wages"],"of unrighteousness;"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.16","order":"03.24.002.26065"},["b","16"],"But was rebuked for his iniquity: the dumb",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"ass"],"speaking with man’s voice forbad the madness of the prophet."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.17","order":"03.24.002.26066"},["b","17"],"These are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"wells"],"without water, clouds that are carried with a tempest; to whom the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"mist"],"of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"darkness"],"is reserved for ever."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.18","order":"03.24.002.26067"},["b","18"],"For when they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"speak"],"great swelling",["i","words"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"vanity"],", they",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"allure"],"through the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_18d"},"lusts"],"of the flesh,",["i","through much"],"wantonness, those that were clean",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_18e"},"escaped"],"from them who live in error."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.19","order":"03.24.002.26068"},["b","19"],"While they promise them",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"liberty"],", they themselves are the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"servants"],"of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"corruption"],": for of whom a man is overcome, of the same is he brought in",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_19d"},"bondage"],"."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.20","order":"03.24.002.26069"},["b","20"],"For if after they have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"escaped"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"pollutions"],"of the world through the knowledge of the Lord and Saviour Jesus Christ, they are",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"again"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_20d"},"entangled"],"therein, and",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_20e"},"overcome"],", the latter end is",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_20f"},"worse"],"with them than the beginning."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.21","order":"03.24.002.26070"},["b","21"],"For it had been better for them not to have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"known"],"the way of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"righteousness"],", than, after they have known",["i","it,"],"to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"turn"],"from the holy commandment delivered unto them."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.22","order":"03.24.002.26071"},["b","22"],"But it is happened unto them according to the true proverb, The dog",["i","is"],"turned to his own",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"vomit"],"again; and the sow that was",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"washed"],"to her wallowing in the mire."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.1a","order":"03.24.002.26072"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-the-early-christian-church"},"TG Apostasy of the Early Christian Church"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-prophets"},"False Prophets"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.1b","order":"03.24.002.26074"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-doctrine"},"TG False Doctrine"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-priesthoods"},"False Priesthoods"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.1c","order":"03.24.002.26076"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/teacher"},"TG Teacher"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.1d","order":"03.24.002.26078"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/6.20"},"1 Cor. 6:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.2a","order":"03.24.002.26080"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/truth"},"TG Truth"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.3a","order":"03.24.002.26082"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/16.18"},"Rom. 16:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.3b","order":"03.24.002.26084"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/32.35"},"Deut. 32:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.3c","order":"03.24.002.26086"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/damnation"},"TG Damnation"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.4a","order":"03.24.002.26088"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/angels"},"TG Angels"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/death-spiritual-first"},"Death, Spiritual, First"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-evil-or-unclean"},"Spirits, Evil or Unclean"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.4b","order":"03.24.002.26090"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/3.6"},"1 Tim. 3:6"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hell"},"TG Hell"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.4c","order":"03.24.002.26092"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/judgment-the-last"},"TG Judgment, the Last"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.5a","order":"03.24.002.26094"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/8.1"},"Gen. 8:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/11.7"},"Heb. 11:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/3.20.20-21"},"1 Pet. 3:20 (20–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.5b","order":"03.24.002.26096"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.5c","order":"03.24.002.26098"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-cleansing-of"},"TG Earth, Cleansing of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/flood"},"Flood"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.6a","order":"03.24.002.26100"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/19.24"},"Gen. 19:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/jude/1.7.4-7"},"Jude 1:7 (4–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.6b","order":"03.24.002.26102"},["b","6b"],["span.small","GR"],"token, example."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.7a","order":"03.24.002.26104"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/19.15.12-22"},"Gen. 19:15 (12–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.7b","order":"03.24.002.26106"},["b","7b"],["span.small","GR"],"oppressed by the outrageous behavior of the lawless."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.7c","order":"03.24.002.26108"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/filthiness"},"TG Filthiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.8a","order":"03.24.002.26110"},["b","8a"],["span.small","GR"],"oppressed, afflicted."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.9a","order":"03.24.002.26112"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/deliver"},"TG Deliver"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.9b","order":"03.24.002.26114"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/godliness"},"TG Godliness"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.9c","order":"03.24.002.26116"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/temptation"},"TG Temptation"],"."],["div",{"id":"9d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.9d","order":"03.24.002.26118"},["b","9d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.5.5-6"},"D&C 38:5 (5–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.9e","order":"03.24.002.26120"},["b","9e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/11.44.41-44"},"Alma 11:44 (41–44)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/12.15.14-18"},"12:15 (14–18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.10a","order":"03.24.002.26122"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-in-darkness"},"TG Walking in Darkness"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.10b","order":"03.24.002.26124"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lust"},"TG Lust"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sexual-immorality"},"Sexual Immorality"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/2.10c","order":"03.24.002.26126"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scri